<div id="review_22629508" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/22629508" />
    <a title="Noran Miss Pumkin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/993934-noran-miss-pumkin"><img alt="Noran Miss Pumkin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1227657007p2/993934.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/22629508?book_show_action=true">May 20, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Noran Miss Pumkin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Noran Miss Pumkin" href="/user/show/993934-noran-miss-pumkin">Noran Miss Pumkin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/993934-noran-miss-pumkin?shelf=ebook">ebook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/993934-noran-miss-pumkin?shelf=2012-books">2012-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/993934-noran-miss-pumkin?shelf=classic">classic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/993934-noran-miss-pumkin?shelf=france">france</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/993934-noran-miss-pumkin?shelf=crime-fiction">crime-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer22629508" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13418740873467039877">I am torn about my rating of the book. Time does not pass evenly, and not still clear about the motives for the murders. Some just robbed, others killed. The trial came and went, without the wife being called. It is a different crime novel for sure. The criminal is quite brilliant, which earns the fourth star. Him vs Sherlock wound a fascinating read!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

