<div id="review_2342187825" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2342187825" />
    <a title="Sylvester" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16779794-sylvester"><img alt="Sylvester" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1609926954p2/16779794.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2342187825?book_show_action=true">Apr 05, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sylvester" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sylvester" href="/user/show/16779794-sylvester">Sylvester</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16779794-sylvester?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16779794-sylvester?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2342187825" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8986118740063417624">Fantomas is a less well known French literary character when compared to Arsene Lupin. First of all, he&apos;s a ruthless villain who kills and secondly, he&apos;s flamboyant and certainly less sophisticated. The writing style is definitely dated, it failed to shock or engage the audience today. It felt like reading a pulp fiction due to the campy tone, but I did enjoy learning about the culture in France at the time.</span>
  <span id="freeText8986118740063417624" style="display:none">Fantomas is a less well known French literary character when compared to Arsene Lupin. First of all, he's a ruthless villain who kills and secondly, he's flamboyant and certainly less sophisticated. The writing style is definitely dated, it failed to shock or engage the audience today. It felt like reading a pulp fiction due to the campy tone, but I did enjoy learning about the culture in France at the time.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8986118740063417624" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


